{"tid":1817445,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"港大學生會向鄧炳強發律師信　沒搜查令須停止進入校園","createTime":"2020-01-09T05:46:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-09T14:10:14.000Z","uid":212626,"like":27,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"df8d06c3496535793a678afe3a32f26f1d64e423","tid":1817445,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T05:46:42.000Z","msg":"香港大學學生會向香港警務處處長鄧炳強發出律師信，要求警方在沒有法庭的搜查令下，停止一切進入校園執法的行動，以及停止一切有可能危害港大師生人身安全的不合理武力。<br />\n<br />\n學生會指出，警方在去年10月初至11月中，先後5次進入及逗留在港大校園範圍，以胡椒噴霧及警棍攻擊學生及校園傳媒，在沒有展示警員編號及沒有向在場學生提供合理的法律基礎之情況下拘捕學生，在沒有被挑釁的情況下向百周年校園發射催淚彈及橡膠子彈，嚴重破壞校園安寧，對港大師生的人身及財產安全構成威脅，因此作出有關行動。<br />\n<br />\n學生會指出，如有任何警務人員作出以上違法行為，不排除展開法律行動。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1501847-20200109.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1501847-20200109.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=y5xLblNGdgzQkswvdzbF01QKcmgIyYy1b1J%2Bn%2Bjwg5M%3D&h=4b415191\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1501847-20200109.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=e0d91134\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1501847-20200109.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"e8e0618cf08a7199a136aca941c018b8a4f2be39","tid":1817445,"uid":286336,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T05:49:55.000Z","msg":"如有？<br />\n<br />\n有咗啦<br />\n<br />\n入稟啦！等乜嘢？"},{"pid":"4431f4eb05bfc51999a0f3dfb186633757da7364","tid":1817445,"uid":236459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T05:50:57.000Z","msg":"借位<br />\n(行動)1月11全民連儂日，有隻雀仔話都想出一分力<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1817431\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1817431</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\nSorry<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa780a4087f246026de3f70216d327c750aee383","tid":1817445,"uid":178364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":